Content Ideas and Strategies
To create impactful content, focus on formats and topics that resonate with individuals in recovery and their families. All content should be trauma-informed, avoiding triggering or judgmental language, and optimized for SEO/AEO with hashtags like #RecoveryJourney, #SoberLiving, #AddictionSupport, and #MentalHealthMatters.
Content Formats
Blog Posts: In-depth articles on recovery strategies, personal stories, and resource guides.
Social Media Campaigns: Daily tips, inspirational quotes, and milestone celebrations on platforms like X and Instagram.
Videos: Short motivational videos or interviews with recovery experts.
Infographics: Visual summaries of recovery tips or resource lists.
Webinars: Live sessions on relapse prevention or mindfulness techniques.
E-books/Guides: Comprehensive resources on specific recovery topics.
Podcasts: Interviews with individuals in recovery or professionals in the field.
