Audience Awareness: Tailor content for diverse audiences, including those in early recovery, long-term sobriety, or supporting loved ones.
Collaboration: Partner with organizations like SAMHSA or local treatment centers for credibility.
SEO/AEO Optimization: Use keywords like “addiction recovery resources” and hashtags to boost visibility.
Accessibility: Ensure content is readable (e.g., clear fonts, alt text for images) and available in multiple formats (PDF, HTML).
Call-to-Action: Include contact info (e.g., Aspire Impact Network’s email or SAMHSA’s Helpline) in all content.
